name: Territorial Sharpjaw
text:
Flood {2}{g}{g}(During your turn, you may pay {2}{g}{g} and exile this card from your hand flooding target land. It loses all land types and abilities, and it gains “{T}: Add {1}.”) 
Whenever you flood Territorial Sharpjaw or it enters the battlefield, target creature you control fights target creature you don’t control.
